1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
ظآزThe breeze of the 1990s drifts byظآز

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
ظآزMemories slowly flicker pastظآز

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
ظآزMy heartbeat
rises and falls with the tuneظآز

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
ظآزThe story quietly begins hereظآز

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
ظآزUnder the dim lights, our eyes meetظآز

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
ظآزTime seems to stand stillظآز

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
ظآزYour smile
breaks through the clouds like sunظآز

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
ظآزMelting the snow deep in my heartظآز

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
ظآزStreet posters spread signals of loveظآز

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
ظآزOur story slowly begins to fermentظآز

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
ظآزHand in hand,
going through every dusk cornerظآز

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
ظآزThe taste of happiness is so subtleظآز

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
ظآزCrossing back to the 1990s stageظآز

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
ظآزYou're my most beautiful surpriseظآز

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
ظآزLove's flame burns within my heartظآز

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
ظآزNot afraid of obstacles aheadظآز

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
ظآزSway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart poundظآز

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
ظآزThis love will never changeظآز

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
ظآزWe hold tight in this crazy eraظآز

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
ظآز1990s love is what we rely onظآز

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,950
=Episode 9=

23
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:00,879
Zhang Guolong.

24
00:02:01,090 --> 00:02:01,840
Where's Zhuang Yan?

25
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:05,079
You really value loyalty and sentiment.

26
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:09,199
I didn't expect you
to come alone for a woman.

27
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:11,879
Since she means so much to you,

28
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:13,520
let's talk about the price.

29
00:02:13,787 --> 00:02:14,708
What do you want?

30
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:18,479
I want all of Jinxin factories

31
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,800
and you to get out of Haicheng.

32
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,599
Sure.

33
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,000
Sure?

34
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,400
No, you...

35
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,560
You just agreed?

36
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:32,080
If I knew you were such a romantic,

37
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,919
why waste energy with you?

38
00:02:33,919 --> 00:02:35,080
I fought you

39
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:37,000
and compete you in business.

40
00:02:38,199 --> 00:02:39,560
Give him the contract to sign.

41
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,759
Before I sign,

42
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,390
you better show me where Zhuang Yan is.

43
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:47,800
She's fine.

44
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,125
Sign the contract first.

45
00:02:49,300 --> 00:02:51,639
Zhang Guolong, do you know
the consequences of kidnapping?

46
00:02:52,450 --> 00:02:54,390
That's not your concern.

47
00:02:54,487 --> 00:02:56,646
Your concern right now is Zhuang Yan.

48
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,159
Qin Mo.

49
00:02:58,599 --> 00:03:01,199
I advise you to obey our boss,

50
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:04,560
or your lover will freeze to death
in this truck.

51
00:03:05,479 --> 00:03:07,560
You talk too much.
It shows your true colors.

52
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,439
Zhang Guolong.

53
00:03:09,159 --> 00:03:10,879
You locked Zhuang Yan
in a freezer truck?

54
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,120
She's perfectly fine.

55
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,199
Sign the contract first.

56
00:03:13,199 --> 00:03:14,759
And we'll let her go.

57
00:03:16,479 --> 00:03:18,080
Go. Fight him!

58
00:03:52,725 --> 00:03:56,363
ظآزThe old dial tone circles in my earظآز

59
00:03:56,488 --> 00:03:59,800
ظآزFaded tickets point to a cicada summerظآز

60
00:03:59,963 --> 00:04:03,550
ظآزThe videotape
whispers your image in the frameظآز

61
00:04:03,850 --> 00:04:07,138
ظآزAgainst the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smileظآز

62
00:04:07,363 --> 00:04:10,988
ظآزI'm a clumsy guest in a frozen sceneظآز

63
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:11,800
Zhuang Yan.

64
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:14,488
ظآزHow do I answer familiar lines?ظآز

65
00:04:14,563 --> 00:04:21,025
ظآزEven one second rewrites missed linesظآز

66
00:04:21,825 --> 00:04:24,079
ظآزRewind to 1995,
back to the street we metظآز

67
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:24,759
Zhuang Yan.

68
00:04:26,175 --> 00:04:29,475
ظآزWind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulderظآز

69
00:04:29,537 --> 00:04:32,837
ظآزI wish I could pause and stop timeظآز

70
00:04:32,837 --> 00:04:36,487
ظآزLet unspoken love
be preserved forever as amberظآز

71
00:04:36,637 --> 00:04:40,787
ظآزRewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertipsظآز

72
00:04:40,875 --> 00:04:44,138
ظآزStar sparks in your eyes burn my chestظآز

73
00:04:44,138 --> 00:04:47,888
ظآزThis illusory script
is beyond my savingظآز

74
00:04:47,888 --> 00:04:53,120
ظآزI can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglassظآز

75
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:53,920
You're awake.

76
00:04:54,425 --> 00:04:55,305
How do you feel?

77
00:04:58,312 --> 00:04:59,079
I'm fine.

78
00:05:03,462 --> 00:05:05,000
You haven't eaten a thing these days.

79
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:06,352
You must be starving.

80
00:05:07,712 --> 00:05:08,839
The doctor said

81
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,759
you can only have plain porridge
that's easily digestible.

82
00:05:20,075 --> 00:05:21,275
I can manage myself.

83
00:05:21,399 --> 00:05:22,360
Don't move.

84
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:26,120
You've been to death's door,
and you're still stubborn.

85
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:03,199
Are your injuries alright?

86
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,079
If I weren't fine,

87
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,750
do you think I'd be sitting here
feeding you porridge?

88
00:06:10,759 --> 00:06:11,759
Are you really alright?

89
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:15,360
It's rare to see you this anxious.

90
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,079
It's kind of amusing.

91
00:06:17,162 --> 00:06:20,962
ظآزStreet posters spread signals of loveظآز

92
00:06:20,962 --> 00:06:24,462
ظآزOur story slowly begins to fermentظآز

93
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:26,480
Alright.

94
00:06:26,700 --> 00:06:28,290
Looks like you still have some strength.

95
00:06:28,700 --> 00:06:30,026
Make sure you finish the porridge.

96
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:32,178
I'll go find the doctor.

97
00:06:33,162 --> 00:06:36,950
ظآزCrossing back to the 1990s stageظآز

98
00:06:36,950 --> 00:06:40,387
ظآزYou're my most beautiful surpriseظآز

99
00:06:40,387 --> 00:06:43,812
ظآزLove's flame burns within my heartظآز

100
00:06:43,937 --> 00:06:45,337
(Three Days Later
Jinxin Food Co. Ltd.)

101
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,560
Planning Department
must keep a close eye.

102
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,600
Consider the preferences
of foreign clients.

103
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:51,480
We need to make them feel our sincerity.

104
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,160
Yes, understood.

105
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,319
What foreign clients?

106
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:56,680
Introducing foreign investment
is Mr. Zhou's key project.

107
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:58,000
Irrelevant people

108
00:06:58,519 --> 00:06:59,639
don't need to be informed.

109
00:07:00,279 --> 00:07:02,759
(In the past life, Zhou Zeyang
relied on foreign investment)

110
00:07:02,759 --> 00:07:04,160
(to secure his position at Jinxin.)

111
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:05,600
(No.)

112
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,180
(I can't let him succeed.)

113
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,519
Ms. Zhuang.

114
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:10,079
Are you feeling better?

115
00:07:10,580 --> 00:07:11,680
You're back to work so soon.

116
00:07:11,879 --> 00:07:12,920
Of course.

117
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:14,920
I need to come back quickly,

118
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,390
or Jinxin will become your territory.

119
00:07:17,319 --> 00:07:18,800
You jest.

120
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:21,600
Mr. Qin entrusted me
with such an important task,

121
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,120
I'll naturally give it my all.

122
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,199
Then you better handle it well.

123
00:07:25,399 --> 00:07:27,720
Don't let down those supporting you.

124
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,759
Alright, almost there.

125
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,959
Take a look at this file.

126
00:07:38,199 --> 00:07:38,680
Alright.

127
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:40,480
I'll confirm it on my side as well.

128
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:43,800
Zhuang Yan.

129
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,519
Where are you going?

130
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,000
Out to get something to eat.

131
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:52,920
I can't stand seeing Zhou Zeyang
with that smug look.

132
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:54,160
Wait a moment.

133
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:55,319
I'll take you.

134
00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:03,199
Mr. Daniels.

135
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:06,519
this is Mr. Qin Mo of Jinxin Food Co.

136
00:08:07,879 --> 00:08:08,800
Mr. Daniels.

137
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:10,000
Welcome to Jinxin.

138
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:10,959
Nice to meet you.

139
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,079
Nice to meet you too.

140
00:08:12,079 --> 00:08:13,212
Mo, we have a problem.

141
00:08:13,212 --> 00:08:15,220
The translator had a car accident
on the way here.

142
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,720
Zeyang doesn't speak English.

143
00:08:16,959 --> 00:08:18,399
I've found a new translator,

144
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:20,070
but it will take them
some time to arrive.

145
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:24,079
What now?

146
00:08:24,425 --> 00:08:26,425
Do you want me to communicate
via sign language?

147
00:08:28,037 --> 00:08:29,040
Mr. Daniels.

148
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:29,959
Yes.

149
00:08:29,959 --> 00:08:31,125
Welcome to Jinxin.

150
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:32,825
My name is Zhuang Yan,

151
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,279
the Sales Manager.

152
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,480
You can call me Paula.

153
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,519
Hello, Paula.

154
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,362
I'm happy you're here

155
00:08:39,362 --> 00:08:42,519
because I thought my trip for today
was meaningless.

156
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:46,559
I apologize for the unpleasant experience.

157
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:47,675
t's okay.

158
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:50,059
I want to introduce our company.

159
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,639
I will be happy to see it.

160
00:08:51,639 --> 00:08:52,120
Come here.

161
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:52,799
Thank you.

162
00:08:54,279 --> 00:08:56,120
This is our office.

163
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:59,799
And our company
has a total of 50 people.

164
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:00,600
Hmm.

165
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,360
Sounds a lot.

166
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,960
Do you feel a little bit hungry?

167
00:09:03,679 --> 00:09:05,159
I want to try something.

168
00:09:05,519 --> 00:09:06,279
Okay.

169
00:09:06,279 --> 00:09:07,240
Special Chinese food.

170
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:09,320
You can try our production.
Okay, this way.

171
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,162
That's a lot.

172
00:09:10,212 --> 00:09:12,525
They are all our production.

173
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:14,799
Which one would you want to taste?

174
00:09:14,799 --> 00:09:16,200
I would like to try this one.

175
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:18,879
This cookie is delicious.

176
00:09:19,399 --> 00:09:20,799
Tell me. Do you like it?

177
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,000
I like it.

178
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,000
I want to try it.

179
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,390
Pleasure doing business with you.

180
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,279
Mr. Daniels.

181
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,879
It's our pleasure cooperating with you.

182
00:09:33,879 --> 00:09:36,450
Oh, it's a pleasure for me.

183
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:39,000
I was so happy being with you together.

184
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,639
Thank you so much.

185
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,200
Thank you.

186
00:09:43,039 --> 00:09:44,519
Li, see him out.

187
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:46,039
- See you next time.
- Bye bye.

188
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,080
Thank you.

189
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,559
Congratulations, Mr. Qin.

190
00:09:53,759 --> 00:09:54,919
With the foreign investment,

191
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:58,240
Jinxin will not only
lead in technology and management,

192
00:09:58,725 --> 00:10:01,703
but also greatly improve
its market and brand influence.

193
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,080
Jinxin

194
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:05,320
becoming the top food enterprise
in the country

195
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,200
is just around the corner.

196
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,919
Why did you call me to the office?

197
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,399
You just recovered.

198
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,120
Eat less instant noodles.

199
00:10:19,130 --> 00:10:19,990
Drink more hot water.

200
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:24,879
Why are you smiling?

201
00:10:26,090 --> 00:10:27,919
"Drink more hot water"
is forbidden in love.

202
00:10:27,919 --> 00:10:29,600
I can't hear that.

203
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:32,759
Love?

204
00:10:40,519 --> 00:10:42,519
I did you a huge favor today.

205
00:10:44,090 --> 00:10:44,960
How will you thank me?

206
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,080
The gift is ready.

207
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,759
Ginseng chicken soup?

208
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:03,279
Is this all?

209
00:11:03,279 --> 00:11:04,080
Trying to brush me off?

210
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:04,799
How stingy.

211
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:06,960
Then what do you want?

212
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,679
No talks about shares.

213
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,960
Then nothing about you
is worth my interest.

214
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,360
You're so sharp-tongued.

215
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:24,879
Am I that bad?

216
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:25,480
Ah.

217
00:11:29,159 --> 00:11:30,399
Drink your soup.

218
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,000
Your English is so good.

219
00:11:34,162 --> 00:11:35,081
Who taught you?

220
00:11:35,519 --> 00:11:37,480
Didn't you send me abroad?

221
00:11:38,279 --> 00:11:39,960
Your English level

222
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,000
is not something
rural education can achieve.

223
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:47,159
Are you doubting me again?

224
00:11:48,825 --> 00:11:50,585
Are you doubting my identity

225
00:11:50,759 --> 00:11:52,600
or this translation mishap

226
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,799
is my doing too?

227
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:55,799
No.

228
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:58,279
Even if you dislike Zhou Zeyang,

229
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,600
you wouldn't harm an innocent person.

230
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,480
Don't think you know me well.

231
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,960
I want to know you.

232
00:12:15,759 --> 00:12:16,960
Will you give me a chance?

233
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,720
Here's a chance.

234
00:12:26,519 --> 00:12:28,279
Go out with me after work tonight.

235
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:31,879
Got it.

236
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:55,200
Hey, Li.

237
00:12:57,679 --> 00:12:58,519
Mr. Qin?

238
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,320
You're still here?

239
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,480
It's almost seven.

240
00:13:02,679 --> 00:13:03,840
Have the others left?

241
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:07,000
They left half an hour ago

242
00:13:07,159 --> 00:13:08,679
to celebrate Mr. Zhou's foreign deal.

243
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:10,990
Then where's Zhuang Yan?

244
00:13:11,519 --> 00:13:12,360
Ms. Zhuang?

245
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,000
She's still here.

246
00:13:17,679 --> 00:13:18,360
Look.

247
00:13:18,679 --> 00:13:20,759
How's this scarf with this coat

248
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,679
and my hairstyle?

249
00:13:23,919 --> 00:13:24,720
Mr. Qin.

250
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,480
I don't know about these things.

251
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:29,799
You really don't.

252
00:13:30,559 --> 00:13:31,360
By the way,

253
00:13:31,919 --> 00:13:33,799
put a full-length mirror here tomorrow.

254
00:13:34,937 --> 00:13:35,738
Oh.

255
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,559
This one.

256
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,799
Remember to remind me to sign tomorrow.

257
00:13:50,879 --> 00:13:52,159
You're still working?

258
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,000
Then...

259
00:13:55,519 --> 00:13:56,279
I'm done.

260
00:13:56,679 --> 00:13:57,480
We can leave.

261
00:14:18,900 --> 00:14:22,100
ظآزRain fog covering the office windowsظآز

262
00:14:22,650 --> 00:14:25,675
ظآزWorking overtime until late at night,
the coffee has turned coldظآز

263
00:14:26,562 --> 00:14:31,012
ظآزThe fax machine
suddenly printed out a line of textظآز

264
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:33,320
Come, follow me. Come.

265
00:14:53,562 --> 00:14:57,200
ظآزThe old dial tone circles in my earظآز

266
00:14:57,325 --> 00:15:00,637
ظآزFaded tickets point to a cicada summerظآز

267
00:15:00,800 --> 00:15:04,387
ظآزThe videotape
whispers your image in the frameظآز

268
00:15:04,687 --> 00:15:07,975
ظآزAgainst the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smileظآز

269
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:11,825
ظآزI'm a clumsy guest in a frozen sceneظآز

270
00:15:11,987 --> 00:15:15,325
ظآزHow do I answer familiar lines?ظآز

271
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:19,112
ظآزI know
the train will leave this stationظآز

272
00:15:19,162 --> 00:15:23,025
ظآزI know the ending's in a faded futureظآز

273
00:15:23,087 --> 00:15:29,137
ظآزYet I want to approach that warmthظآز

274
00:15:30,312 --> 00:15:37,050
ظآزEven one second rewrites missed linesظآز

275
00:15:37,337 --> 00:15:41,612
ظآزRewind to 1995,
back to the street we metظآز

276
00:15:41,612 --> 00:15:44,912
ظآزWind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulderظآز

277
00:15:44,987 --> 00:15:49,287
ظآزI wish I could pause and stop timeظآز

278
00:15:49,350 --> 00:15:53,000
ظآزLet unspoken love
be preserved forever as amberظآز

279
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:56,562
ظآزRewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertipsظآز

280
00:15:56,612 --> 00:15:59,875
ظآزStar sparks in your eyes burn my chestظآز

281
00:15:59,875 --> 00:16:03,625
ظآزThis looping script
is beyond my savingظآز

282
00:16:03,625 --> 00:16:10,337
ظآزI can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglassظآز
